# @dependency-start
# contract environment
# responsibility Pins the managed renderer bundle protocol, Node runtime, and direct package versions.
# downstream configuration ./package.json direct renderer package declarations
# downstream configuration ./package-lock.json exact renderer dependency graph
# downstream implementation ../scripts/install-managed-bundle.sh POSIX bundle installer
# downstream implementation ../scripts/install-managed-bundle.ps1 Windows bundle installer
# downstream tool ../scripts/check-ptymark-runtime-dependencies.mjs version alignment gate
# @dependency-end

